title: Southwest Airlines - available seat miles 2011 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing ASMs in billions, containing a total of 9 data points.
In general ASMs in billions has rose over the Year.
ASMs in billions is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2012, roughly constant from 2012 to 2014, gradually increasing from 2014 to 2017, and finally roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum ASMs in billions, about 159.8 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest ASMs in billions, of value 120.58 was reported at Year 2011
